Contribute
content
ds.content represents to a small content of the page, over here you can add the title for your page, with some body.

Example:

Input
null
-- ds.content: Built for the next generation of small business

Fastn is an all-in-one payments platform where businesses can connect, transact,
and grow together.

-- ds.content: Built for the next generation of small business

Fastn is an all-in-one payments platform where businesses can connect, transact,
and grow together.
Lang:
ftd
Output
Built for the next generation of small business
Fastn is an all-in-one payments platform where businesses can connect, transact, and grow together.

Properties of content component

  • title - type: caption It‚Äôs used to add title to content component.
  • body - type: body It‚Äôs used to add body content to content component.
